CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 15, 1955, pg. 10 reads: "AKA's Complete Plans - Members of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority's Cotillion committee are shown or the last lap of their plan-making for the fourth Debutante Cotillion which will take place at Gateway Plaza, Feb. 11. Left to right: Elizabeth McCombs, chairman of invitation committee; Edna L. Garrison, co-chairman of the Cotillion; Evelyn Waters, chairman of decorations; Hazel T. Carter, invitations and contact committee. - Harris photo snapped in Gateway Plaza."
TitMainTitle: Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority's Cotillion committee, left to right: Elizabeth McCombs, Edna L. Garrison, Evelyn Waters, Hazel T. Carter,  gathered around table in Gateway Plaza
